reviewText: This video is just sick its one for the collection.
Very well done film on graffiti. There's a lot of information about the history and current realms of this subculture of art. I've watched this about 6 times since purchasing it over a year ago.
This documentary gave a wonderful, in depth and insightful view of street art around the globe. It was playful yet serious, and jam packed with just pure awesomeness. HIGHLY recommended!
